sp. in France (
<bibRefCitation author="Roumeguere, C" journalOrPublisher="Systematic Biology" pageId="0" pageNumber="147" publicationUrl="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/11828914" refId="B67" refString="Roumeguere, C, 1891. https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/11828914" url="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/11828914" year="1891">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Roumeguère">Roumeguere</normalizedToken>
1891
